<lb n="1"/>cakaṉ kālamāyirattu nāṉūṟṟe
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṇpattāriṟ kalati cūḻnta ceka
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṅkaraṇa virattākki cittirai
